  <h2>TL;DR — 3-Minute Summary</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Most scheduling problems are not calendar problems.</strong> They are lead capture, phone tag, and follow-up problems.</li>
    <li><strong>Standalone employee scheduling software only solves part of the issue.</strong> What most Wichita service businesses actually need is <mark>workflow automation</mark>.</li>
